About The HackathonHackAlliance is an eight weeklong university-wide hackathon organised by NTU College of Engineering in partnership with Dell. HackAlliance can benefit you in the following ways…
Provides participants with real-world situations to solve
Widens participants’ social networking through mentorship by Dell industry professionals
Participants will be equipped with necessary skillsets for the fast-moving world
The chance to win exciting Dell products and internship opportunities*

Learn product management & business communication skills from product ideation and development to marketing* Please note that actual placements are not guaranteed for the full-time/internship opportunities. It will be dependent on the candidate’s fit during interviews.WHY SHOULD YOU JOIN?
